      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained. The exterior looks great with a nice shine, though you'll find a few minor stone chips and some light surface scratches upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only typical signs of light use. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has been regularly serviced, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
